for(int i = 0; i &lt; array[0].length; i++) {
    for(int j = 0; j &lt; array.length; j++) {
        System.out.print(array[j][i]);
    }
    System.out.println();
}
```

You have to make sure that [ArrayOutOfBoundException](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/lang/ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException.html) is not thrown by not mixing rows and columns indices.
